original: Lindberg, Carl-Gustav Gabriel, komminister, Linköping, f. 24/3/81 i Björkvik, Södermani. L, av foiksk :lär. Anders Gustaf L. o. Charlotta Brinck. G. 10 m. Jenny Marie-Louise Gustafson. Barn: Sten f. 14, ing. v. SAAB, Linköp., Gertrud 15, g. m. major Henrik Nordström, Gbg. — Stud:ex. i Sthlm 19, prästv. f. Linköp. stift 21. Ständig adj. i S:t-Anna 21-27, kyrkoadj. i Linköp. 27, kommin. där sed. 40.
translated: Lindberg, Carl-Gustav Gabriel, clergyman, Linköping, b. 24/3/81 in Björkvik, Södermani. Son of farmer Anders Gustaf L. and Charlotta Brinck. Married on 10/ m. Jenny Marie-Louise Gustafson. Children: Sten b. 14, working at SAAB, Linköping, Gertrud b. 15, married to Major Henrik Nordström, Gothenburg. — High school graduation in Stockholm 19, ordained as a priest for Linköping diocese in 21. Permanent curate in S:t-Anna 21-27, vicarage curate in Linköping 27, serving as curate there since 40.
